7 7.1.2 EU863-870 ISM Band channel frequencies

8 In Europe, radio spectrum allocation is the ISM band is defined by ETSI [EN300.220].

9 The network channels can be freely attributed by the network operator. However the three 10 following default channels must be implemented in every EU868MHz end-device. Those 11 channels are the minimum set that all network gateways should always be listening on.

12

